---
import '../styles/global.css';
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
import ScrollToTop from '../components/ScrollToTop.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <SEO 
      title="About"
      description="Through poetry and reflection, I seek to illuminate the words we struggle to say, the emotions we find difficult to name, and the experiences we all quietly share."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <style>
        body {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        
        .nav-header {
            background: rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.8);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }
        
        .author-photo {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid var(--border-subtle);
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">
    
    <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-md nav-header">
        <nav class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16 sm:h-20">
                <a href="/" class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-light tracking-widest" style="font-family: var(--serif); color: var(--text-primary);">
                    INAAYAT
                </a>
                <div class="flex gap-4 sm:gap-8 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light">
                    <a href="/poems" class="transition-colors" style="color: var(--text-secondary);" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--text-primary)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text-secondary)'">Poems</a>
                    <a href="/stories" class="transition-colors" style="color: var(--text-secondary);" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--text-primary)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text-secondary)'">Stories</a>
                    <a href="/gallery" class="transition-colors" style="color: var(--text-secondary);" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--text-primary)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text-secondary)'">Gallery</a>
                    <a href="/about" class="transition-colors" style="color: var(--text-primary);">About</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="mb-16 text-center">
                <!-- Author Photo - CHANGE THIS IMAGE -->
                <img 
                    src="/images/author.jpg" 
                    alt="Suri Rathod"
                    class="author-photo"
                />
                <!-- To change your photo: replace /public/images/author.jpg with your photo -->
                
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-light mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-family: var(--serif); color: var(--text-primary);">
                    About Inaayat
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    An expression of reality — Words that often go unspoken
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                
                <div class="mb-12 leading-relaxed text-lg" style="font-family: var(--serif); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 2;">
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        We carry countless emotions through the chaos of daily life—moments of joy, 
                        sorrow, wonder, and longing that often remain unspoken. In the battle of our 
                        busy existence, these feelings linger silently within us, waiting for expression.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        <span style="font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-blue);">Inaayat</span> 
                        is my effort to give voice to those untold stories and unfinished conversations. 
                        Through poetry and reflection, I seek to illuminate the words we struggle to say, 
                        the emotions we find difficult to name, and the experiences we all quietly share.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        This space is an attempt to express what is usually left unsaid—to capture the 
                        subtle beauty of everyday moments and the profound depth of human feeling. Each 
                        piece is a conversation with silence, an effort to transform emotion into language.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="mb-8">
                        I hope you find pieces of yourself here. I hope these words resonate, comfort, 
                        or inspire. Your presence means the world, and your feedback helps me grow with 
                        every word I write.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="text-center text-xl" style="font-style: italic; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                        Thank you | शुक्रिया
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center mt-12 pt-8" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
                    <p class="text-2xl font-light mb-2" style="font-family: var(--serif); color: var(--text-primary);">
                        — Suri
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 pt-12 text-center" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-light mb-6" style="font-family: var(--serif); color: var(--text-primary);">
                    Stay Connected
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-8 font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    Follow the journey on Instagram or share your thoughts
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/_._.inaayat._._/" target="_blank" 
                       class="inline-block px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-all" 
                       style="border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); color: var(--text-primary);"
                       onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--text-secondary)'; this.style.background='var(--bg-accent)'"
                       onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border-subtle)'; this.style.background='transparent'">
                        Instagram
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://x.com/suri_rathore_?s=21" target="_blank"
                       class="inline-block px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-all" 
                       style="border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); color: var(--text-primary);"
                       onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--text-secondary)'; this.style.background='var(--bg-accent)'"
                       onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border-subtle)'; this.style.background='transparent'">
                        X (Twitter)
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="py-12" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm font-light" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <p>© 2017-{new Date().getFullYear()} · All Rights Reserved</p>
                    <span>·</span>
                    <a href="/copyright" class="transition-colors" style="color: var(--text-muted);" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--text-primary)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text-muted)'">Copyright Policy</a>
                </div>
                <p>Inaayat</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <ScrollToTop />

</body>
</html>